title: Dutch art dealer discovers first 'new' Rembrandt in 44 years
text:
Dutch art dealer discovers first 'new' Rembrandt in 44 years 1:21pm EDT - 00:46
The first 'new' Rembrandt since 1974 is put on display at the Hermitage museum in Amsterdam after being discovered by a Dutch art dealer at an auction house in 2016. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
